    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TolE0192">
<l>tāṉyā ṉeṉṉu māyī riṟutiyu</l>
<l>mēṉmup peyaroṭum vēṟupā ṭilavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In the endings of <foreign xml:lang="ta">ellārum</foreign> which denotes the third person,</l>
<l>and of <foreign xml:lang="ta">ellīrum</foreign> which denotes the second person,</l>
<l>the consonant and the sound <foreign xml:lang="ta">u</foreign> disappear ;</l>
<l>so it is said ;</l>
<l>the non-vocalized consonant <foreign xml:lang="ta">r</foreign> must remain ;</l>
<l>and <foreign xml:lang="ta">um</foreign> stands as final ;</l>
<l><foreign xml:lang="ta">tam</foreign> comes in between in the third person</l>
<l>and <foreign xml:lang="ta">num</foreign> comes in between with the words of the second person.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
